univention-samba (6.0.19-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * In a samba4 domain use the 'native' samba4/ntacl/backend,
    i.e. configure vfs module acl_xattr with for all file shares.
    In this case remount all ext3 and ext4 filesystems with user_xattr.
    In standard UCS setups this affects only memberservers (Bug #25248)

 -- Arvid Requate <requate@univention.de>  Wed, 07 Dec 2011 15:16:33 +0100

