univention-samba (6.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Package cleanup for UCS 3.0 (Bug #22561)
    * Bump version for UCS 3.0
    * Replace univention-baseconfig with univention-config-registry
    * Replace static UCR header in the UCR templates with '@%@UCRWARNING=#
      @%@'
    * Update copyright to 2011
    * Update to debhelper 7
    * Switch from python2.4 to python2.6
    * Add ucslint
  * Removed univention-samba-ha and univention-samba-bdc
  * Removed old pdc-takeover scripts and tools

