univention-samba (5.0.15-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * On a slave pdc the local samba account for the passdb ldap backend
    needs the permission to add a samba objectClass to the host object.
    By default the ldap/hostdn is used as passdb ldap backend  but he
    does not have these permissions. So the join user will be used as
    passdb ldap account temporarily. Bug #19128

 -- Stefan Gohmann <gohmann@univention.de>  Sat, 31 Jul 2010 15:10:50 +0200

univention-samba (5.0.14-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * use univention.password for password quality checks. Bug #14943

 -- Stefan Gohmann <gohmann@univention.de>  Tue, 27 Jul 2010 21:12:19 +0200

univention-samba (5.0.13-1) unstable; urgency=low

  [Roman Asendorf]
   * adding attribute sambaPasswordHistory if missing (Bug: #14908)
   * adding attribute sambaAcctFlags if missing (Bug: #14908)
   * changed pw expiry date calculation from ucr based to policy based (Bug: #14908)
   * added support for sync of pw expire dates from nt to ucs (Bug: #14908)

 -- Stefan Gohmann <gohmann@univention.de>  Fri, 23 Jul 2010 17:30:43 +0200

